Package model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IStockMarketModel
    The interface IStockMarketModel which has methods to buy stocks, calculate cost basis, view composition, create and evaluate portfolio.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Services
    The class Services which has methods to get data for a particular ticker, check the nearest date in case of holidays and get a value for a company.
    StockMarketModelImpl
    The class StockMarketModelImpl which implements the interface IStockMarketModel.
    User
    The class User which has methods to buy stock, create portfolio, evaluate portfolio, calculate cost basis and view composition of the portfolio.
